The '''''Worldhopper''''' was the [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]] owned by [[Rennik]] and crewed by his [[Rennik twins|twin sons]]. In [[9 ABY/Legends|9 ABY]], it brought the [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] [[Astromech droid/Legends|astromech droids]] [[Whistler]] and [[R5-G8/Legends|Gate]] to [[Oradin]], a [[City/Legends|city]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Brentaal IV/Legends|Brentaal IV]].

